{"tid":1758352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[抵撚死啦] 撐警大聯盟召集人冼澤正病逝","createTime":"2019-11-27T04:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T12:51:09.000Z","uid":236891,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2e57fd0cc611075bd57b72dcdc9662bccf5496e6","tid":1758352,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-27-2019/57871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-27-2019%2F57871&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=b93fb0ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-27-2019/57871</a><br />\n<br />\n傻鳩「撐警大聯盟」召集人、退休高級督察冼澤正因病離世。 網上消息指，冼澤正患病約三個月，剛過了64生日，於昨日（11月26日）黃昏因病去世。 冼澤正與李偲嫣曾帶領「正義聯盟」、「撐警大聯盟」與「香港家長聯會」到嶺南大學抗議，不滿該校早前一個音樂會上有樂隊唱粗口歌辱警；又曾就近月示威活動，拍片支持警察。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-27-2019/57871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-27-2019%2F57871&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=b93fb0ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-27-2019/57871</a>"},{"pid":"5c71750f2d883bff0d79d9edc62d718838e7d19f","tid":1758352,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b965343c320db05a88196722cf284a94b9935a4e","tid"